    <title><custom ref="synthesis-actividad-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <q>¿Por qué B es diferente?</q>  (It doesn’t have 20 dots.)
      </li>
      <li>
        <q>¿Cómo encontraron el número total en cada imagen?</q>  (In D, I counted every dot. In C I counted by 5 since each row had 5 dots. In A, I counted by 5 since each row had 5 squares. In B, I just added 20 and 4 for the extra column.)
      </li>
    </ul>
